    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:0",
      "text": "Sampling tab 会通过以下设置",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:1",
      "text": "Max Samples",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:3",
      "text": "Pixel Variance",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:5",
      "text": "Integrator",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:7",
      "text": "Default Ray Depths",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:8",
      "text": "Clamping",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:9",
      "text": "Russian Roulette",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:10",
      "text": "（可用于缩短 path lengths）以及",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:11",
      "text": "Filtering",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:13",
      "text": "在窗口顶部的 Presets menu 中，有 draft、production 等 sampling presets。此外，你也可以在那里保存自己的 sampling presets。",
      "ascii_letters": 56,
      "cjk_chars": 23
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:16",
      "text": "IPR Samples",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:17",
      "text": "IPR samples 为 IPR rendering 提供独立的 Max Samples 和 Pixel Variance。默认情况下，它设得低于正式 render settings，以便快速反馈。",
      "ascii_letters": 59,
      "cjk_chars": 25
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:19",
      "text": "Progressive Pixels",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:20",
      "text": "注意：在 XPU mode 下运行 IPR 时，如果将 Interactive Refinement 设为高于 1，会激活 Progressive Pixels。",
      "ascii_letters": 48,
      "cjk_chars": 17
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:21",
      "text": "Integrator",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:23",
      "text": "Integrator",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:25",
      "text": "PxrPathTracer",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:27",
      "text": "有关各 integrator 设置的信息，请参阅各 integrator 页面：",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 14
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:28",
      "text": "PxrDefault",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:29",
      "text": "PxrDirectLighting",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:30",
      "text": "PxrOcclusion",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:31",
      "text": "PxrPathTracer",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:33",
      "text": "PxrValidateBxdf",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:34",
      "text": "PxrVisualizer",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:35",
      "text": "Default Ray Depths",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:36",
      "text": "Max Specular Depth:",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:37",
      "text": "reflections 和 refractions 的 bounce 次数。除非需要 multi bounce effects，或有 panes of glass/windows，否则值 1 或 2 已经足够。此 attribute 可以在单个 objects 上 override。",
      "ascii_letters": 89,
      "cjk_chars": 25
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:38",
      "text": "Max Diffuse Depth:",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:39",
      "text": "indirect illumination 的 diffuse bounces 数量。值 1 通常足够；更大的值会更慢。此 attribute 可以在单个 objects 上 override。",
      "ascii_letters": 58,
      "cjk_chars": 22
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:42",
      "text": "用于控制 rendered pixels 的",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:44",
      "text": "。box、triangle、disk、gaussian 和 blackman-harris 是 softening filters；catmull-rom、sinc、mitchell、separable-catmull-rom、lanczos 和 bessel 是 sharpening filters。Separable-catmull-rom 是一个不错的折中选择。",
      "ascii_letters": 143,
      "cjk_chars": 14
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:45",
      "text": "Filter Size:",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:47",
      "text": "Integrator Overrides",
      "ascii_letters": 19,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:49",
      "text": "在 Render Setup 中创建所需 layer，并确认当前处于这个 layer（visible 已勾选，即 eyeball icon）",
      "ascii_letters": 39,
      "cjk_chars": 19
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:50",
      "text": "在 Render Settings 中为此 layer 选择要使用的 integrator。这会创建所需 node。",
      "ascii_letters": 33,
      "cjk_chars": 16
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:52",
      "text": "\"Create Connection Override for Visible Layer\"",
      "ascii_letters": 39,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "6dcc2e0355:53",
      "text": "4. 要连接这个新的 integrator，只需在 menu 中键入你选择的 integrator 名称，并在名称后添加 .msg。例如输入：PxrOcclusion.msg，然后按 Enter/Return。这会连接 integrator，并且 override 会在 Render Settings 中以 Orange highlight 显示。",
      "ascii_letters": 100,
      "cjk_chars": 45
    }
  ],
